values:
So, can anyone guess what I do before a party?&nbsp; It doesn't involve getting ready for the party, and actually takes a lot of time away from getting ready for it.&nbsp; 

Last night, we did our 2nd annual open house for our coworkers.&nbsp; Thank heavens I got some last minute help, since I didn't start getting ready for the party till noon.&nbsp; Turned out fantastic and everyone had a good time.&nbsp; Made some awesome food, and had a good time visiting with coworkers outside of work.&nbsp; 

Today's been a lazy day.&nbsp; Going to Coffee with the Bears at 4.&nbsp; Figuring out what to whip up for dinner tonight.&nbsp; That's about it.

How was your weekend?
